data.description: Open House, Saturday, Dec. 2,   1- 4pm.  WOW!!! OVER A QUARTER OF AN ACRE INSIDE 1604 OFF THOUSAND OAKS!  PRETTY 2 STORY ON CORNER LOT OFFERS IT ALL! HIGH CEILINGS, LIVING ROOM WITH FIREPLACE. STUDY/OFFICE BEHIND FRENCH DOORS HAS SEPARATE OUTSIDE ACCESS (COULD WORK AS 4th BEDROOM). AMAZING, PARTY FRIENDLY SIZE KITCHEN AND DINING AREA WITH LARGE ISLAND, THAT OPENS TO A BIG DECK AND BEAUTIFUL,  BACKYARD. BACKYARD IS A GARDENER'S DELIGHT WITH GREENHOUSE AND BEDS READY TO GO. NEWER HIGH END HVAC SYSTEM.  FANTASTIC NEIGHBORHOOD, CLOSE TO SHOPPING, GREAT RESTAURANTS, ETC..  EXCELLENT SCHOOLS!
